Explorers look at Smart Record 3.52 Introducing Siri Shortcuts. Use Siri any time to start a new recording. Create new recording on iOS with Siri Go to Settings Siri Search All Shortcuts to create your own custom Siri commands for Smart Record. It works with Shortcuts app as well! You can automatically start recording when the meeting starts and stop recording at the end of the meeting. Apple Watch Complications Smart Record supports all types of watch faces. We can t wait to add it to your Apple Watch! Split Recording Split your recordings into two parts by tapping top right button Split in the playback screen. Fixed Skip Silence feature in some cases. Enhanced Spotlight Search Search Recordings by titles or notes directly on your iPhone or iPad.
Explorers look at Smart Record 3.51 We re thrilled to announce a new Apple Watch app. No need to have iPhone near when recording. Isn t that a great addition
